343 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
POP MUSIC CHARTS: THAT'S SHOW BIZ 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Some people were sure Madonna's career would suffer after her X-rated 
appearance on David Letterman's TV show. Obviously these people don't buy her 
records--but others still do. Her single "I'll Remember" is No. 2 on The Times' 
Southern California pop singles chart and No. 6 nationally. Reba McEntire 
