<P>
 * I found Ron Harris' column particularly insightful ("The Riots Helped No One 
-- Except the Well-Placed Few," April 29).The headline would suggest that those 
who rioted, such as then-20-year-old Damien, haven't prospered much since April 
29, 1992. 
