<P>
 Jennifer Bundy, 13, is about to go on a shopping spree at the Buenaventura 
Mall, compliments of the Ventura Police Department. 
</P>
<P>
 On Friday, the Anacapa Middle School seventh-grader placed first among about 
50 entries in a poster contest for the Police Department's annual block 
