</P>
<P>
 "The idea kind of popped into my mind right after they made the announcement 
about the contest," Jennifer said. 
</P>
<P>
 All four middle schools in Ventura participated in the contest, and police 
were surprised at the high level of interest, Purnell said. Jennifer's poster 
will be used to promote next year's block party, Purnell said. PEGGY Y. LEE 
