<TEXT>
<P>
 A fair designed to help potential home buyers in the low- to moderate-income 
bracket will be held Saturday from 9 a.m. to 3 p.m. at the Los Angeles 
Convention Center. Admittance is free. 
</P>
<P>
 Sponsored by the Southern California Mortgage Bankers Assn., HUD and the 
National Assn. of Real Estate Brokers, the fair will feature more than 75 
