EMPLOYEE ORDERED INTO ROBBER'S CAR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Police said they were looking for an employee of a Mexican-style market 
Saturday after the man was ordered to get into a robber's getaway car. 
</P>
