<HEADLINE>
<P>
PLAY ON RIOTS ADDED TO LIBRARY COLLECTION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Anna Deavere Smith's one-woman theater work based on reaction to the first 
Rodney G. King beating trial has been added to a collection at the USC Doheny 
Memorial Library that documents the 1992 riots. 
</P>
<P>
 Titled "Los Angeles: A City in Stress," the collection is open to the public. 
Call (213) 740-5192. 
</P>
