<HEADLINE>
<P>
BESCHEN MAKES FINALS AT HUNTINGTON BEACH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Shane Beschen of San Clemente qualified for the finals of the Katin Team 
Challenge surfing competition Saturday on the north side of the Huntington 
Beach Pier. 
</P>
<P>
 Four top pros advanced to today's finals, including world champion Kelly 
Slater. 
</P>
<P>
 Tag-team quarterfinals begin at 7 a.m. today, with individual and team finals 
beginning at noon. 
</P>
