<P>
Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA050894-0357 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 039900 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
May 8, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 6; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
