<P>
NEWS, TIPS & BARGAINS; INDEX FOR THE 'BEEN THERE' CROWD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 For the traveler who's "been there, done that" comes the spring/summer issue 
of "Specialty Travel Index," a guide to more than 180 special interest 
activities in more than 200 states and countries. 
</P>
<P>
 From bungee jumping and breweries to caving and cooking schools, includes a 
directory of more than 630 special-interest tour operators worldwide, with 
program descriptions, addresses and telephone and fax numbers. Tour operators 
pay to be listed, but it's a lot of information in one place. The index is 
published twice a year. Single copies are $6; subscriptions are $10 a year. For 
information: Specialty Travel Index, 305 San Anselmo Ave., San Anselmo, Calif. 
94960. 
