<P>
 An article about Isabella Rossellini last Sunday incorrectly identified her 
twin sister. Ingrid Rossellini, a professor of medieval literature at Princeton 
University, is the actress's twin. Pia Lindstrom, an entertainment critic based 
in New York, is their older half sister. 
